posts.post_title: Want to Buy: 1879-80 NY Clipper Newspaper Woodcuts
posts.post_content:
Posted By: Phil Garry
I am looking for any HOF'ers that were included in the woodcuts issued by NY Clipper Newspaper during the 1879-1880 seasons (these are catalogued in the 2009 Standard Catalogue of Baseball Cards). If anyone has any for sale, please e-mail me privately at: vguerrerobb@yahoo.com
